Class DefaultBundle

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.apache.logging.log4j.core.impl.DefaultBundle
  • public class DefaultBundle
extends Object
    Contains default bindings for Log4j including support for PropertiesUtil-based configuration.
    See Also:
    Log4jPropertyKey, ContextSelector, ShutdownCallbackRegistry, Clock, NanoClock, ConfigurationFactory, MergeStrategy, InterpolatorFactory, ContextDataInjector, LogEventFactory, StrSubstitutor
